Whether you're familiar with Homestuck or not, friendsim is a super fun exploration of the HS expanded universe. Between all the volumes, there are enough characters for there to be something for everyone. My favs are cirava, tagora, and remele! The staff are clearly passionate, and have put a lot of love into all the writing & assets. And a dollar per volume is a more than fair price for the content! IMO, homestuck being placed under the creative direction of its fans is a semi transformative experience and you wouldn't think it would turn out so well but it really has
